  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Interleukin-1 antagonists such as canakinumab have been used for the treatment of AOSD and
      have had a marked influence on the activity of the disease, including joint mobility. Results
      from controlled clinical studies are not, however, currently available.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
